2017 — SpecNext Ltd. Z80N

Compatible extension of the Zilog Z80, used as the FPGA of the ZX Spectrum Next.

Address space
16-bit
I/O space
16-bit

Main table

  • Green marks new instructions to the Zilog Z80.
  • Red marks new instructions replacing earlier ones for the Zilog Z80.
  • Orange marks instructions present but undocumented in Zilog Z80 and documented for the SpecNext Ltd. Z80N.
  • Pink background marks undocumented instructions.
  • Plum background marks duplicate instructions.
